{"id":11430,"date":"2013-01-17T13:13:22","date_gmt":"2013-01-17T18:13:22","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=11430"},"modified":"2019-05-23T11:19:05","modified_gmt":"2019-05-23T07:19:05","slug":"dhimmah-muslims-wahidah","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/17\/dhimmah-muslims-wahidah\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Covenants: Civil protection of the Muslims is one"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Ali Ibn Abi Talib reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<b>The protection of the Muslims is one; they strive to fulfill it among the least of them. Whoever betrays a Muslim, upon him is the curse of Allah, the angels, and the people altogether. His obligatory and voluntary good deeds will not be accepted<\/b>.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>In another narration, the Prophet said, \u201c<b>The lives of the believers are equal. They strive to fulfill the covenant of the least of them, and they give support against whoever opposes them<\/b>.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: al-<span class=\"il\">Sunan<\/span>\u00a0al-Kubra\u0301 15464<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <em><strong>Sahih<\/strong> <\/em>(authentic) according to Al-Albani<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a\u064d\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e<b> \u0630\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0651\u0629\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0633\u0652\u0644\u0650\u0645\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064e \u0648\u064e\u0627\u062d\u0650\u062f\u064e\u0629\u064c \u064a\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0649 \u